    <string name="help_content">Frequently asked questions\n\n1. How do I find nearby places?\nOpen the Maps tab from the dashboard.\n\n2. How do I save a visit?\nGo to Settings → Visit receipts and fill in the form.\n\n3. How do I report a problem?\nUse Submit a complaint from Settings.\n\n4. How do I log out?\nOpen Settings and tap Log out.</string>
    <string name="privacy_content">Relaxhub Privacy Policy\n\nWe collect account information you provide during registration and feedback you submit in the app. Location data is used only to show nearby places on the map.\n\nYour data is stored securely in our database and is not sold to third parties. Contact support if you want your account removed.</string>
